  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/e444cdcc353ced2703c4ca56c3559fcd.webp?t=1659069890\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/e444cdcc353ced2703c4ca56c3559fcd.poster.avif?t=1659069890\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=45 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/d6e5e19a77e35eaa0a646d17f182487d.avif?t=1659069890\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br><br>The virus broke out in the city. It came so quickly that most residents have no time to evacuate before the lockdown. <br><br>You are one of them. You have to survive among other survivors, parades and zombies and escape before it’s bombed by the government.<br><br>It could be a strategy or a shooting game. You could build defense works and deploy manpower. <br><br>In spare time, you may also build campsites to keep campfires, sleeping bags, store materials and place survivors. Don’t forget to raise chickens and plant fields to make a living!<br><br>Game features:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/1baff19dd2d75105883af7745ff8248f.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br>       survival ，In the game, you can pick up a variety of materials, such as building materials, such as bricks, wood, which are used to build obstacles, <br>          camps and so on, which can help to defend the enemy.<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/dc5f75da0045c361f4277a2ef05eea27.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=158 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/2477a2f7b918de0ac1380df1810ff459.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br>       Strategy play, you can control your teammates and arrange their positions for defensive operations. All fortifications and manpower deployment in the <br>           game will be designed and built by players<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/1ce28823f3b47667ef3a73c5a84685a7.poster.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/1ce28823f3b47667ef3a73c5a84685a7.webm?t=1659069890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/1ce28823f3b47667ef3a73c5a84685a7.mp4?t=1659069890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/7a5bbe2908578f3d27294bd06308d075.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br>       Craft. Besides fighting, the game also contains survival elements. You can farm and raise chickens or trade to obtain survival materials.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/d9df51475788029829b5c416bead140a.poster.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/d9df51475788029829b5c416bead140a.webm?t=1659069890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/d9df51475788029829b5c416bead140a.mp4?t=1659069890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/608af1535d6d8d7db889b6ce47b85ef7.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br>       Tower defense, in addition to combat by yourself, you can also choose strategic tower defense.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/b3d772b8d81131c3b1b03605d5a15659.poster.avif?t=1659069890\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/b3d772b8d81131c3b1b03605d5a15659.webm?t=1659069890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1353250/extras/b3d772b8d81131c3b1b03605d5a15659.mp4?t=1659069890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
